RHINOX/SNIPER


RHINOX looks at Prowl, "you could say I am new, well new to neo beast 
wars as you may say it. I am RHINOX form the original Beast Wars. Do 
you know me or did you leave to Neo Beast wars before We got back." 
Rhinox looks around. He exam the war room. Nothing like the war room 
on the Axalon but ofcoarse The war room on The axalon was on the 
bridge so you never really had to move to one room to the other. 
RHINOX realize he doesn't know who the lead bot is. "Hey who incharge 
here errrrrr who is here? So far I only seen 2 or 3 people." RHINOX 
looks at the chairs it sits down in one at the back. "When does this 
meeting gets started?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

SNIPER looks at Striker and at Arcangel. He spits at the ground next 
to Arcangel's right foot. "Well Prowl called for us Striker, lets go! 
ohhh wait, Arcangel do you want to stay here? Or do you want to
leave. 
Your choice." SNIPER turns around and heads for the Ark's war room.
